    {
      "id": "flip-reset",
      "name": "Flip Reset",
      "description": "In the air, orienting the car's wheels to touch the ball. When three or more wheels make contact, the player's flip timer is reset, granting an unlimited second flip (dodge) in the air. Falling off the ball is preferred as jumping off activates the standard 1.5-second flip timer.",
