        "Shay"
      ],
      "perform_instructions": "Get an initial flip reset. Rotate your car so the nose points sideways relative to the ball. Perform a backward diagonal flip into the ball to make wheel contact and secure another reset.",
      "correction_notes": "Updated to clarify sideways rotation + backward diagonal flip mechanics. Increased difficulty to 90 and reduced viability to 10 as it's primarily a freestyle/style mechanic."
    },
    {
      "id": "jakze-reset",
      "name": "Jakze Reset",
      "description": "An upside-down front flip that is immediately flip-canceled into the bottom-right or bottom-left, depending on the car's initial tilt during the front flip. If the wheels are tilted left, a down-right flip cancel is used; if tilted right, a down-left flip cancel is used.",
      "category": "flip_reset",
      "type": "air",
      "difficulty": 85,
      "viability": 20,
      "tags": [
        "flip_reset",
